				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/Ai-Nh%E1%BB%8B-Th%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%BA/poem-nHHf8iIeresXmdhEV-ABLA">Ai Nhị Thế phú - 哀二世賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/author-HC1oHxsir20vL_KcVXiEhQ">Tư Mã Tương Như</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-D%E1%BB%A5c-Thu%C3%BD-s%C6%A1n/poem-on-zCgA1CG9fN1pbNRwlpA">Đề Dục Thuý sơn - 題浴翆山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Mi%E1%BB%87n/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-ho%E1%BA%A1-mai/poem-xOogqNjbaXknquxnAP16aQ">Đề hoạ mai - 題畫梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Mi%E1%BB%87n/author-fEGcjpEMDS77hLL_7VN-Wg">Vương Miện</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-K%E1%BA%BF-Vi%C3%AAm/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Ki%E1%BB%81u-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng/poem-YH3D_E4lYMP2QOQ4qq7mtw">Đề Ngọc Kiều động</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-K%E1%BA%BF-Vi%C3%AAm/author-LCpLBSvLevySQCPd4caRzg">Hoàng Kế Viêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Chi-V%E1%BA%A5n/K%C3%BD-Thi%C3%AAn-Thai-T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-Th%E1%BB%ABa-Trinh/poem-jzM1CVBr-ONKK_wnPYSnpQ">Ký Thiên Thai Tư Mã Thừa Trinh - 寄天台司馬道士</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Chi-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-ugO5moh7gzYYDOe2gVJzDg">Tống Chi Vấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/Nam-%C3%94ng-m%E1%BB%99ng-l%E1%BB%A5c-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-fyhCR98oGwWB23vOD9LFiw">Nam Ông mộng lục tự - 南翁夢錄序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/author-_vSGbKXOej4AgRYmpqgykw">Hồ Nguyên Trừng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-V%C4%83n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/Ng%E1%BB%A5c-trung-b%E1%BA%A5t-thu%E1%BB%B5/poem-G5dUxP9B1ELoYUeV8qY5gw">Ngục trung bất thuỵ - 獄中不睡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-V%C4%83n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-lAWWG_aVUUofuj7GzUYcmQ">Hoàng Văn Tuấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/Tam-Thanh-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng/poem-F3nFvV3Mk_jLjWFAMJwfKA">Tam Thanh động - 三清洞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-III/poem-EsyilYBXJVcg5eoS7vsfEA">Vô đề (III) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/author-bg2Iw4F0Q1WB-Vf8_0Kqcw">Khả Mân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Thanh-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-t8ceGQaUvFAomirH_IzMQg">Xuất dương - 出洋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Thanh-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-H7U7KCvecgO1KzCd1kGc9A">Phan Thanh Giản</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
